	quests: [
		{
			dependencies: ["3ABDA0A1EA25EB8F"]
			description: ["Pam's HarvestCraft adds over 80 crops across every biome — each biome holds seeds you cannot find elsewhere. The agave crop grows in warm and arid regions; its juice is a Farmer's Delight cooking ingredient. Beyond food, Pam's crops provide raw inputs for Mine & Slash alchemy, Soul Land pill crafting, and every advanced Cooking Pot recipe. Many Pam's crops self-seed if left to mature, so a diverse farm propagates itself without seed repurchasing. Your farm is your supply chain — diversify it before you need it."]
			id: "22C4FB700C4C7B5F"
			rewards: [
				{
