			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			description: ["The Farmer's Delight Skillet handles single-ingredient or two-ingredient recipes directly on any heat source without water input. Bacon, fried eggs, and grilled vegetables cook individually in seconds. The Skillet is required for prep steps in multi-stage FD recipes — several Cooking Pot inputs must first be processed through a Skillet before they become valid cooking ingredients. Keep one beside the Cooking Pot; they are complementary, not redundant."]
			id: "5BB7359037AA2B78"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "4657DF2123CCD9B4"
