			title: "Skillet"
			x: -1.0d
			y: 2.5d
		}
		{
			description: ["Chicken Soup requires chicken, carrot, cabbage, and water — a multi-crop recipe with one of the highest saturation-to-ingredient ratios in Farmer's Delight. For extended dungeon runs or Mine & Slash map clears, stock twelve servings before departure. The combination of Regeneration from Vegetable Soup and full saturation from Chicken Soup keeps your health loop passive across most combat encounters. Food buff effects stack additively with Mine & Slash stat soul investments."]
			id: "186340035E2EB2D7"
			optional: true
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
