			title: "Hoes and Hoegression"
			x: -6.0d
			y: -2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["0487B5BA7036BFC5"]
			description: ["Farmer's Delight Rich Soil turns any farmland into enhanced-yield soil — crops grown on it have a chance to drop double seeds on harvest, enabling a self-seeding loop without repurchasing. Rich Soil is produced by composting organic matter in a FD Organic Compost block over time. Feed it with excess crop outputs and harvest scraps. Replant your core crop plots on Rich Soil farmland to eliminate seed supply as a long-term concern — once the loop is seeded, it runs without input."]
			id: "7C0130C974E8C937"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
