			title: "Soul and Mana Converge"
			x: 10.0d
			y: -5.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000002"]
			description: ["Tertium Essence is crafted from 2x Prudentium Essence. It gates Tier 3 resource seeds — iron, gold, diamond, and coal in the first class, with nature and elemental essences following. Each T3 seed requires 4x Tertium Essence plus the corresponding material. Once planted on Mystical Soil with Growth Accelerators beneath, a T3 crop produces 1–2 essence per harvest cycle. A row of eight iron seed plots with ten Accelerators each will outpace a Macerator's input throughput within a few hours of unattended operation."]
			id: "1A2B3C4D00000003"
