			dependencies: [
				"1A2B3C4D00000003"
				"72158F0D783153BE"
				"27B707D2E3E3ED14"
			]
			description: ["Imperium Essence carries a resonance that reacts to living alloys and sacrificial altar power. Terrasteel, born from the convergence of Manasteel, Livingrock, and Elven dust via the Terrestrial Agglomeration Plate, carries a spiritual signature that stabilizes higher-tier essence growth. Pair it with a functional Blood Altar and the Imperium growth band unlocks. Botania and Blood Magic share overlapping resonance profiles in the essence matrix — reaching T4 requires you to have mastered both."]
			id: "1A2B3C4D00000004"
