		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000004"]
			description: ["Imperium Essence opens access to rare ore seeds — copper, tin, lead, silver, and nickel in the first wave, with redstone and rarer materials following. Craft it from 2x Tertium Essence. For passive automation, pair a Create Mechanical Harvester over Imperium-seeded rows with a Drawer Controller and overflow filtering into GTCEu item pipes. The output curve at this point begins to exceed casual mining returns — this is where the farm becomes an industry, not a supplement."]
