				"4470A64D131B98EF"
			]
			description: ["The Gaia Guardian is Botania's ultimate test — a magical boss summoned on a Natural Altar that demands mastery of the mana system and serious combat preparation. Defeating it proves your magical development has reached a level sufficient to stabilize Tier 5 growth matrices. The Spirit King cultivation rank represents a parallel spiritual attainment; together, the two milestones produce the combined resonance that permits Supremium growth. Prepare a large flat area, Mana Tablets, and Pixie Dust supplies before summoning."]
