		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000006"]
			description: ["Supremium Essence is the pinnacle of standard Mystical Agriculture. From it, seeds for titanium, platinum, tungsten, chromium, and uranium become craftable — materials that would otherwise require deep GTCEu ore processing chains or dangerous dimensional mining. Each Supremium seed requires 8x Supremium Essence plus the target material. Supremium also converts into Mystical Fertilizer, which instantly matures any MA crop — build a stockpile before planting your endgame rows."]
