			description: ["Insanium Essence from Mystical Agriculture Additions is an engineered essence — it requires the LP reservoir of an Archmage's Blood Orb and Spirit Ancestor cultivation rank to stabilize. The Archmage's Orb provides the stored life energy needed for the growth ritual; Spirit Ancestor attainment signals that your soul has entered a resonance tier capable of sustaining the unstable Insanium matrix. Once both thresholds clear, Insanium seeds become craftable — covering the final tier of exotic materials."]
