			title: "Essence Replicator"
			x: 25.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000021"]
			description: ["The Essence Enhancer upgrades essence tiers using chemical reagents — crown ethers and cryptand complexes produced through GTCEu's organic chemistry chain. At maximum tier, the Enhancer accepts Awakened Supremium and reagents to produce Insanium at rates not achievable through standard crop farming. The chemistry for the reagents (ethylene oxide → glycol → triglycol → crown ether synthesis) is deep GTCEu work, but the output — a reliable Insanium tap — is worth the process."]
			id: "1A2B3C4D00000022"
			rewards: [{
				count: 10
				id: "3A2B3C4D00000022"
