		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000009"]
			description: ["The Awakened Supremium Helmet provides strong defense and MA charm slots — insert charms for passive effects like Night Vision, Step Assist, or Fire Immunity. Assembled directly from Awakened Supremium Essence and Dragon's Breath at a standard crafting table; no Smeltery or special workbench required."]
