		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000009"]
			description: ["The Awakened Supremium Chestplate carries the highest defense value in the MA armor set and the largest charm capacity. Available charms include Flight, Water Breathing, and Absorption — each a passive effect while worn. A Flight charm-equipped chestplate makes this armor competitive for dimensional exploration well before Elytra access."]
