		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000023"]
			description: ["The Awakened Supremium Leggings provide movement augmentation via charms — Sprint Charm gives permanent Speed I; Wither Resistance prevents the Wither effect from reducing max health during Mine & Slash dungeon runs. A full Awakened Supremium set with Absorption and Sprint charms creates a mobile tank build that works across most combat encounters without Soul Land cultivation stat investments."]
			id: "1A2B3C4D00000025"
