		{
			dependencies: ["1A2B3C4D00000024"]
			description: ["The Awakened Supremium Boots carry Jump Boost and Fall Damage immunity charms. With the full armor set assembled, you have a complete magical-tier defense suite that predates the need for GTCEu Hazmat suits or Blood Magic Living Armor. Both remain competitive for specialized use cases, but the full Awakened set is a strong baseline for EV-tier GTCEu content and dimensional exploration requiring sustained survivability."]
